      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice 1/4 <span class=\"text-purple\">[1/3]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1/2]</span> of your<strong> red onion </strong>and set aside for later</p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>remaining red onion</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways and scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon, throw the watery seeds away and chop the <strong>deseeded</strong> <strong>cucumber </strong>into half moons</p>",
