    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat and once hot, add the <strong>diced red onion </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle more oil if your pan is looking a little dry!</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
