    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>ginger</strong> to the pan with your <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong>, and<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[255ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
