    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the pan with <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until thickened slightly</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add your <strong>naan[s] </strong>to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p>",
