      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Combine the<strong> chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>cucumber half moons</strong>, <strong>sliced red onion</strong> and a pinch of <strong>chopped coriander</strong> in a bowl with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato salad</strong></p>",
