      "instruction": "<p>Return the<strong> golden paneer</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add your<strong> natural yoghurt</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until everything's warmed through</p><p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir through the <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong> – this is your<strong> achari paneer</strong></p>",
